data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ****SWIMMING POOL HOME!!***  PRICED TO SELL AT $270,000!***WELL BELOW LOCAL MARKET FOR SIMILAR STYLE POOL HOME***** Well laid out split 2 bedroom, 2 bath, pool home with 2 car garage is ready for its new owner.***   This split floor plan home also has the convenience of an inside laundry room with plenty of room for storage.  Home does need some TLC, allowing its new owner to make it their own. New roof 2/23, HVAC replaced 9/17, septic inspected and pumped out 2022. THIS HOME WOULD MAKE A PERFECT PEMANENT HOME, GREAT VACTION HOME OR EXCELLENT RENTAL PROPERTY! Close to shopping, restaurants, hospitals and I-75.
